{"tid":1566732,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你執到人銀包，拎哂啲錢唔緊要，最少都畀返啲證件同嗰銀包人啊！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-13T17:15:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T09:31:42.000Z","uid":263038,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2b62fdeb7e9241e3b837726e238c49a9a59da25","tid":1566732,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:15:56.000Z","msg":"執到銀包<br />\n就算你攞完入面啲錢<br />\n最起碼都放返嗰銀包去櫃檯or狗鐵or郵筒or保安<br />\n反正實拉唔到你<br />\n如果懶得拎去嘅話<br />\n攞完入面啲錢咪原地放返低囉<br />\n點解要成個攞走or dom落垃圾桶？<br />\n攞完錢仲要成個銀包袋走or dom落垃圾桶<br />\n呢個行為完全係損人不利己<br />\n咁撚冇品嘅一撚定係廢老or新移民or支那人<br />\n我祝你地下代世世代代都瘋狂唔見銀包<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005be9f062300e6f30fb90f219270e2fbb09d60d","tid":1566732,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b148617ff573c9d21cfe796957a7bd9a70523b1","tid":1566732,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9860f7ac993528a36c5095e52277d18a29360772","tid":1566732,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69e580b4b12d98ea5aa1e6cee68eda76d0883664","tid":1566732,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adde813283934c64d930f95a5376576b30fbfaa0","tid":1566732,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2798337fed048bb7a1790c0e1343d30124bd834","tid":1566732,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:19:39.000Z","msg":"<img sr